title: Neutrogena Blackhead Eliminating Daily Scrub, 4.2 Ounce
description: Neutrogena Blackhead Eliminating Daily Scrub clears blackheads and helps prevent new ones to give you clear, smooth skin. Its powerful combination of blackhead fighting medicine and microbeads works together to clean pores and help keep them free of blackheads: Salicylic acid penetrates into pores to remove blackhead causing dirt and oil, gentle exfoliating beads sweep away dead skin cells, skin soothing beads deliver conditioners to help prevent skin from overdrying.
